thread.title: Nikkei Down 0.5%; Caution Weighs Ahead of Data
thread.title_full: Nikkei Down 0.5%; Caution Weighs Ahead of China GDP Data - WSJ

author: Kosaku Narioka
title: Nikkei Down 0.5%; Caution Weighs Ahead of Data
text: 0041 GMT [Dow Jones] Japanese stocks are down, weighed by caution ahead of China’s third quarter gross domestic product data. Fears about deterioration in the Chinese economy have helped cause stock selloffs over the summer. Market participants are worried about any potential downside risk to Japanese corporate earnings results stemming from slower Chinese growth. Still, “at the same time there are some expectations for economic stimulus measures,” says Yoshihiro Okumura, general manager of research at Chibagin Asset Management....
